data.text:
Releases: Early 2000’s

Country of origin: USA

Material: Paper, PP

Size: approx. 410mm x 27mm (original print ad) / A3 (Laminating Pouch Film) / 175 Mic Thickness

Details: Laminated print art with mate finish

Condition: Because an original copy of the advertisement has been used (and not a reprint), the paper may have some deterioration. After laminating it looks much better, however there may be scratches on the finished piece. This product is sold as used.
